            "title": "Germany's composite PMI hits 3-month high in June",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li id=\"description\">Composite PMI in Germany increased to 50.40 points in June, a 3-month high, from 48.50 points in May.<p id=\"description\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p id=\"description\">Services PMI in Germany increased to 49.70 points in June from 47.10 points in May of 2025. </p></li>\n</ul>\n<p>ETFs: (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EWG\" title=\"iShares MSCI Germany ETF\">EWG</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GF\" title=\"New Germany Fund Inc.\">GF</a></span></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FGM\" title=\"First Trust Germany AlphaDEX® Fund ETF\">FGM</a></span></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DAX\" title=\"Global X DAX Germany ETF\">DAX</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FLGR\" title=\"Franklin FTSE Germany ETF\">FLGR</a></span></span></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-